{"id": 2314, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪些影视剧里妈妈形象的塑造会让你一秒出戏？", "description": "你在影视剧里发现过哪些关于妈妈的刻板印象？（题图来自：iStock©CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 379, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180507174306iHoelFQyvKa0k1LX.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-11T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 279047, "content": "《我的前半生》里子君的妈妈干涉女儿和身边人的感情", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 279048, "content": "《恶作剧之吻》里的直树妈妈想尽办法安排孩子的人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 92, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 279049, "content": "《夏洛特烦恼》之类爱情剧里总需要一个不讲理唱反调的主角妈妈", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 281425, "content": "相亲", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1257902}, {"id": 281426, "content": "平凡岁月里沙溢的姑奶奶，为了沙溢结婚，不惜动用欺骗，霸王硬上弓，生米煮熟等手段，最后，还嫌弃人家…迷之相像", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1257902}, {"id": 281429, "content": "大嘴娘麻将桌发威虐展堂\n展堂妈新婚夜心理测湘玉\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1316658}, {"id": 281430, "content": "大嘴娘麻将桌发威虐展堂\n展堂妈新婚夜心机验湘玉", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1316658}, {"id": 281431, "content": "将军在上？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 523416}, {"id": 281432, "content": "花师奶", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898883}, {"id": 281447, "content": "《咱们结婚吧》里面演高圆圆的妈的张凯丽！一张口说话我就头疼！", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1312821}, {"id": 281451, "content": "她妈跟模特一样时时刻刻十分美艳，我咋没有这样的妈妈，我也没见过不好意思。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1232483}, {"id": 281452, "content": "《我的前半生 》罗子君她妈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288801}, {"id": 281455, "content": "《花样男子》，筑紫的父母完全是卖女儿，就算女儿要被强奸也不管不顾，道明寺的妈妈也无意儿子硬做各种安排。所有影视剧里的父母不顾孩子意愿擅自做过分的安排都让我出戏和恼火", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1085613}, {"id": 281457, "content": "“你吃吧，妈不饿”", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341423}, {"id": 281458, "content": "Dddisj", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341430}, {"id": 281464, "content": "一副苦相", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189259}, {"id": 281465, "content": "一副操劳命", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189259}, {"id": 281466, "content": "永远在操心", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189259}, {"id": 281467, "content": "事儿妈脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189259}, {"id": 281469, "content": "《经常请吃饭的漂亮姐姐》里的女主妈妈总觉得是自己老公没有出息，没有成为一个高官才让女儿嫁不出的，并且总认为是女儿不好的原因才导致和渣男分手的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341495}, {"id": 281470, "content": "那种特别性感特别风骚的。风云里面，聂风的妈！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232644}, {"id": 281474, "content": "没有意见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341522}, {"id": 281475, "content": "换个颜色", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341522}, {"id": 281477, "content": "杉菜的妈妈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297456}, {"id": 281478, "content": "大多数影视剧的妈妈形象", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1339680}, {"id": 281481, "content": "犹如反派存在一样的，一生都在为子女操劳提供根本不需要的帮助的，认为到了婚嫁年龄不结婚都是反人类的妈妈，没错我说的都是在座的国产电视剧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277878}, {"id": 281492, "content": "忘了啥国剧，妈妈比女儿还年轻，嘴里却一副老成持重的口吻", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901407}, {"id": 281502, "content": "跋扈至极", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717805}, {"id": 281512, "content": " 鸟?", "image": "img/option/option/20180512064645ja2QNJSO4v58RhZK", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225922}, {"id": 281513, "content": "《欢乐颂》里樊胜美的妈妈，重男轻女", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341731}, {"id": 281514, "content": "为了一个家日夜都在外面奔波", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1248176}, {"id": 281515, "content": "所以母親節就快到了搞這個是要幹嘛，聚集仇恨？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341879}]}